description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity to join an experienced District Nursing Team in the Ty Bryn District Team in Caerphilly Borough . Would you like to care for patients in their own home working collaboratively with Health CareProfessionals, third sector and local authority to deliver seamless care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited from enthusiastic individuals who are passionate about developing their career and providing high standards of nursing care to people within their own homes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Individualised education packages will be devised to ensure you are equipped with the necessary skills and develop the confidence to work autonomously and be part of this forward thinking motivated team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date: 12th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gaynor Tudor&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;sister&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gaynor.tudor@wales.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
